<plot>Inspired by the heroic odyssey of Jeanne d'Arc, In Her Mother's Eyes follows Isabelle d'Arc as she takes to the streets in search of her estranged child Joan. United in grief, their dreams echo in the voices of countless mothers whose children are lost to the daily brutality of the streets. Music selections are derived from the theatrical musical, The Divine Heretic, by Tara Raquel Cates and Kevin Ralph Nelson.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?261697</url></doc>
